{"tid":701910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"律政司轉介警方跟進網上辱罵法官彭寶琴言論","createTime":"2018-06-14T12:53:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T13:05:17.000Z","uid":75156,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4171cc1bd0acfcafee71cb0bbb9ca01903efac96","tid":701910,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T12:53:43.000Z","msg":"包括本民前前發言梁天琦在內的3名涉及2016年旺角騷擾案的被告，日前被法庭判囚3年半至7年不等，其後網上出現負責案件的法官彭寶琴「起底」並作出辱罵。律政司今日回應時表示，司法機構對此高度關注，並已將事件轉介律政司跟進，而律政司就將事件轉介執法部門跟進。<br />\n<br />\n律政司表示，社會人士有權在法律容許的範圍內就法院的裁決或相關事項，發表理性的意見或作出有根據的討論，但仍須遵守法律和尊重司法獨立。律政司強調對法官作任何人身攻擊，惡意或侮辱性批評，或作出任何會損害司法獨立或構成藐視法庭的行為，絕不容許。<br />\n<br />\n就有公眾人士對彭寶琴法官作出可能構成藐視法庭言行一事，律政司已將相關事件轉介有關執法部門跟進。律政司現階段不宜進一步評論有關事宜的具體進度及處理方向，但必定會依據《檢控守則》及適用法律和相關證據公平地處理，並會繼續與執法機構跟進相關事宜。<br />\n<br />\n早前有網民於Facebook發帖，張貼彭寶琴的相片，並附上「原來是警嫂」，文中指其丈夫為前水警警司歐陽國基，於2016年疑因隱性心臟病在西灣河住所身亡，引來其他網民聲討。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180614&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58319047\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180614%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58319047&d=lWNmadnI4Ab5oPcz7c8hgBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=1cf364f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180614%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58319047&h=6c5e215a\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180614&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58319047</a><br />\n<br />\n原來之前果位巴打講嘅係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec583117d44af013b65bd606afa3d50959ea74c","tid":701910,"uid":176111,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T12:54:55.000Z","msg":"高志森拉咗未吖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母律政師<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6f179cc90bfd80bb996ea59c6c849a52347035","tid":701910,"uid":78349,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T12:55:19.000Z","msg":"讚頌=理性<br />\n批評=辱罵=警方跟進"},{"pid":"24ed1e6822a89cfd061775e94eb5ca3f4634d3d7","tid":701910,"uid":75156,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T12:55:51.000Z","msg":"big brother is watching you<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大把網絡欺凌你又唔去執法"},{"pid":"6e315fde82f937902a791fea8b56a859c8cc8db5","tid":701910,"uid":176111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T12:56:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高志森拉咗未吖？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母律政司<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"c3a94e7632f11886c881f12efed6ef47578b7cb9","tid":701910,"uid":15135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T12:58:01.000Z","msg":"停止講有關法官既無謂野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/700794/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/700794/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n巴打原來無吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b2e78f5bb450ef849a2c83b90cc3ac0ebe68d1","tid":701910,"uid":2447,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c3a94e7632f11886c881f12efed6ef47578b7cb9","tid":701910,"uid":15135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T12:58:01.000Z","msg":"停止講有關法官既無謂野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/700794/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/700794/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n巴打原來無吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"ci